text: The Château de Cornod is a Gothic Revival château in Cornod, Jura, Franche- Comté, France. ==History== It was built in 1876 to the design of architects Henri Despierre and Henri Feuga.French Ministry of Culture: Château de Cornod ==Architectural significance== It has been listed as an official historical monument by the French Ministry of Culture since 1971. ==References== Category:Châteaux in Jura (department) Category:Monuments historiques of Bourgogne-Franche-Comté Category:Houses completed in 1876
title: Château de Cornod
